>\n而且冇咗偵探元素，sherlock嘅優點就係會落手落腳搵證據，唔係推理完就算"},{"pid":"c656d2e7a2b28bcb5e406d3f9722f69a626d2fa8","tid":84032,"uid":36958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"我想知最後Sherlock同佢妹係咁拉小提琴個到係想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ee9e3fcaf99076f9068e3be01d3dd339c2eece","tid":84032,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知最後Sherlock同佢妹係咁拉小提琴個到係想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢細妹終於肯open up?<br />\n因為前面Mycroft有講過，佢返去之後個情況仲差過以前"},{"pid":"fea86fb1c95a9f1ee1325756674e7a82f035f30c","tid":84032,"uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得突然間多左個妹呢下真係好撚牽強<br />\n仲要有咩理由會唔記得自己有個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aeaa6d98378a11f49adf270d7126db448beb258","tid":84032,"uid":47724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知最後Sherlock同佢妹係咁拉小提琴個到係想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間佢地見面eurus咪話其實係佢教sherlock拉小提琴既<br />\n之後最尾sherlock去探佢<br />\n佢拉一段 eurus 又拉返同一段 <br />\n我理解係 eurus教緊sherlock拉<br />\n兩姊弟透過小提琴去溝通/建立返關係"},{"pid":"dcc81cd65bb291171b2be9064afc9bd262bc507e","tid":84032,"uid":36958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想知最後Sherlock同佢妹係咁拉小提琴個到係想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間佢地見面eurus咪話其實係佢教sherlock拉小提琴既<br />\n之後最尾sherlock去探佢<br />\n佢拉一段 eurus 又拉返同一段 <br />\n我理解係 eurus教緊sherlock拉<br />\n兩姊弟透過小提琴去溝通/建立返關係</blockquote><br />\n我睇個陣係覺得Sherlock係到彌補以前冇同eurus玩 不過你講係eurus教Sherlock拉小提琴應該係岩 因為第一次見面個陣eurus都話Sherlock係識拉 <br />\n不過我最想講既係 好撚急咩屌你老母 我想睇耐d 結局交代多d得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35bf902dc1411783f1ee989e0d835158866d2f9","tid":84032,"uid":36958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"係套戲入面 第一次Sherlock扮死 搞到John好唔開心 好sad 關係變到好差 但Sherlock就覺得冇乜野 唔係一回事 之後Mary死左 Sherlock覺得好崩潰 好頹 ......依個轉變位真係好好睇 我次次都好回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過以後都冇得再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚唔開心啊啊啊"},{"pid":"82f9d1690d54f2933239bd7b732425e81986822b","tid":84032,"uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係套戲入面 第一次Sherlock扮死 搞到John好唔開心 好sad 關係變到好差 但Sherlock就覺得冇乜野 唔係一回事 之後Mary死左 Sherlock覺得好崩潰 好頹 ......依個轉變位真係好好睇 我次次都好回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過以後都冇得再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚唔開心啊啊啊</blockquote><br />\n第3季第2集已經feel到Sherlock變左<br />\n佢比speech 一開頭我已經係覺得「仆街 一定好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n點知最後佢講啲野好撚感人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跳舞個到都係！"},{"pid":"436e999d7a95ad1844cd3085dbb015641895a4db","tid":84032,"uid":14675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:22:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XvdSlRZ3mRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXvdSlRZ3mRU&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c4195e64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XvdSlRZ3mRU</a>"}]}